<GlobalLayout class:list={["bg-white"]}>
    <section class="flex flex-col items-center py-16 text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-[Noto_Serif_Display] text-[#004346] mb-10">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <div class="max-w-3xl w-full mx-auto px-4 sm:px-8 md:px-16 lg:px-24 text-[#004346] text-left space-y-6">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2">Privacy and Data Protection</h2>
            <p>Daily Bazzar is committed to safeguarding your personal data in accordance with applicable Indian data protection laws, including the Information Technology Act 2000, its allied rules, and the Digital Personal Data Protection Act 2023 (once effective). We collect, store, and process personal information such as your name, address, contact details, and transaction history to provide our Services and improve our offerings. We do not sell or rent your personal data to any third party.</p>
            <p>Your data is shared only with trusted partners (such as payment processors and delivery providers) as necessary to fulfill your orders. All payment transactions are encrypted and processed via secure channels. We employ reasonable security practices to protect your data, including encryption, access control, and regular audits.</p>
            <p>Daily Bazzar uses cookies and similar technologies to enhance your experience. You may disable non-essential cookies through your browser or device settings, but certain features may become unavailable as a result.</p>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2">Fraud Prevention and Security</h2>
            <p>Daily Bazzar actively monitors transactions to detect and prevent fraud. We may, at our sole discretion, refuse to process orders that appear suspicious or fraudulent. We reserve the right to verify customer information or request additional identification prior to fulfilling certain high-value or high-risk orders.</p>
            <p>Customers are responsible for safeguarding their account credentials and must notify us immediately of any unauthorized activity. Daily Bazzar will not be liable for losses resulting from unauthorized use of your account due to your failure to protect your credentials.</p>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2">Modifications to Policy</h2>
            <p>Daily Bazzar reserves the right to modify this Privacy Policy at any time at our sole discretion. Any changes will be posted on the Platform, and the revised Policy will become effective immediately upon posting. It is your responsibility to review this Policy periodically. Continued use of the Platform after any such changes constitutes your acceptance of the revised Policy.</p>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2">Contact Us</h2>
            <p>If you have any questions, concerns, or feedback regarding this Privacy Policy or your data, please contact us at:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc ml-6">
                <li>Email: <a href="mailto:admin@dailybazzar.com" class="text-[#0094BD] underline">admin@dailybazzar.com</a></li>
                <li>Phone: +919954059514</li>
                <li>Address: JB Road, Jorhat - 785001, Assam, India</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </section>
</GlobalLayout>